# Runtime artifacts spawned when bin/cctally-alerts-test runs
# under HOME=<scratch>/<scenario>. The harness rebuilds the SQLite
# {stats,cache}.db fresh into a --out scratch dir, so they are NOT
# committed (gitignored at the repo root; see #97). The committed
# per-scenario tree is:
#   <scenario>/input.env
#   <scenario>/.gitignore
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.log
